div.summary:
The Pennsylvania Conference of the United Brethren in Christ convened in
                    Cumberland County on January 16 and met through the 20th. J.M. Bishop leads the
                    Chambersburg District. In position in stations are: Chambersburg--J. Dickson;
                    Orrstown--J. Baltzell; Big Spring--Z.A. Colestock; Rocky Spring--J.W. Bard. In
                    charge of circuits are: Greencastle--A. Tripner; Alto Dale--N. Altman;
                    Mercersburg--S. Young; Path Valley--L. Mickey; Shippensburg--Wm. Humberger;
                    Bethany Mission--J. Walt.
